General Information

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Celery is a premium quality formula containing celery seed to assist with rheumatism and gout.

Rheumatism Support: Traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine for its anti-rheumatic properties, celery seed can assist with complaints of rheumatism.

Gout Support: Celery seed has been traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine to provide support for gout-like complaints.

Diuretic Properties: Traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine as a diuretic. A diuretic action can help the elimination of waste substances from the body.

Nervous System Tonic: Traditionally used in Western Herbal Medicine as a nervine tonic. Nervine tonics help strengthen, nourish and relax the nervous system.

Swisse Ultiboost High Strength Celery has been formulated based on traditional evidence to provide a premium quality, high strength celery seed formula in a convenient one-a-day dose.

Size: 50 Pack

Ingredients

EACH CAPSULE CONTAINS:

CELERY (Apium graveolens) extract equiv. dry seed 5 g

CELERY SEED OIL 2 mg

Directions

ADULT DOSAGE:
One capsule daily or as directed by a healthcare professional.

STORAGE INSTRUCTIONS

Store below 25 degrees Celsius. Do not use if cap seal is broken.
